"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:12:02.000Z","msg":"junk food<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ad7de948447b8d68cd90639f7e628e9897f87e","tid":278334,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:15:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7be9d4df0ef377db9c144925e0498f7dbf1f90f1","tid":278334,"uid":122152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:15:48.000Z","msg":"M記岀過最撚好鍾食嘅包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af072f6a19289afb1a3d30a1e63a9fc610cb1b27","tid":278334,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:16:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前食過佢個秦脆辣炸雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然味道麻麻,但係起碼D醬有秦國味<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係今次呢個自稱&quot;秦脆&quot;,但係一D秦國味都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n醬係沙律醬加牛肉醬,牛肉小小乾,但係真係幾大舊下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n晚市6點後買個餐送杯芭菲,其實姐係大杯新地加OREO<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以40蚊黎講,都算抵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我寧願佢送多啲薯條或雞翼<br />\n唔食甜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你可以簡拎雪糕卷之後比老母食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee56cf745d116c249568471cbdb6a082f30a9d1","tid":278334,"uid":48358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:18:10.000Z","msg":"影到咁不如唔好影"},{"pid":"d276955162d634dbfdf4a8b12bbdaf896661f7ed","tid":278334,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上次去買無送比我，係咪12點後無"},{"pid":"cb9230aa7a7f868e7